[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 1.791,
    "text": "♫ Whatever happened to predictability"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.789,
    "endTime": 5.472,
    "text": "♫ We live in San Francisco"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.472,
    "endTime": 7.527000000000001,
    "text": "♫ And we're all family, yeah ♫"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.527,
    "endTime": 8.386,
    "text": "- I've never seen it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.386,
    "endTime": 10.405,
    "text": "I don't know what it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.406,
    "endTime": 12.253,
    "text": "- The kid would be like, \"You got it dude.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.253,
    "endTime": 13.947,
    "text": "And that's why I didn't watch it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.947,
    "endTime": 15.503,
    "text": "- So this is the middle child, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.503,
    "endTime": 17.069,
    "text": "Stephanie? (scoffs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.069,
    "endTime": 19.515,
    "text": "Classic middle child, trying to drive the car. Am I right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.515,
    "endTime": 21.361,
    "text": "- This will not end well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.361,
    "endTime": 23.056,
    "text": "- (laughs) What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.056,
    "endTime": 24.322000000000003,
    "text": "- Right into the kitchen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.322,
    "endTime": 27.31,
    "text": "- (laughs) Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.31,
    "endTime": 34.583999999999996,
    "text": "- What kind of a household is this that the youngest child is the first one to come in after a car has just come in through the kitchen?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.584,
    "endTime": 37.126000000000005,
    "text": "- Uncle Jesse wants to get laid (laughs)."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.126,
    "endTime": 39.623,
    "text": "- You know what I love when a sexy girl comes into my room?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.623,
    "endTime": 40.702,
    "text": "A laugh track."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.702,
    "endTime": 42.107,
    "text": "(laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.107,
    "endTime": 43.86,
    "text": "- Do people get nightmares from watching this show?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.86,
    "endTime": 45.207,
    "text": "'Cause I think I might tonight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.207,
    "endTime": 47.505,
    "text": "- You don't want your family showing up in your sex dream."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.505,
    "endTime": 50.106,
    "text": "- Now, is that the dead mom who's back, or is that the prostitute?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.106,
    "endTime": 52.508,
    "text": "- You need serious psychological evaluation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.508,
    "endTime": 54.238,
    "text": "- Oh, God."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.238,
    "endTime": 55.57,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.955,
    "endTime": 63.440999999999995,
    "text": "- John Stamos must have woken up every single day of his life and just kissed the mirror and been like, \"Thank you.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.441,
    "endTime": 64.544,
    "text": "- He's so attractive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.544,
    "endTime": 68.76899999999999,
    "text": "- I feel like he would have been my childhood crush if it wasn't Arnold from Hey, Arnold."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.769,
    "endTime": 72.44900000000001,
    "text": "- The babies are naked. Oh, weird (laughs)."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.449,
    "endTime": 75.503,
    "text": "- So this isn't a parody of anything?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.503,
    "endTime": 77.36,
    "text": "This is really in the show?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.897,
    "endTime": 81.539,
    "text": "Great hairstyles."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.539,
    "endTime": 83.397,
    "text": "I feel like we should bring some of that back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.397,
    "endTime": 86.218,
    "text": "- It feels like a parody of itself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.218,
    "endTime": 89.956,
    "text": "Maybe that's because it was really influential for the time and it was important?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.956,
    "endTime": 91.08200000000001,
    "text": "I can respect that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.082,
    "endTime": 92.835,
    "text": "Or maybe it's just really, really bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.835,
    "endTime": 94.262,
    "text": "We may never know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.263,
    "endTime": 96.04,
    "text": "- If I'd known that it was this crazy,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.04,
    "endTime": 97.58300000000001,
    "text": "maybe I would have watched it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.583,
    "endTime": 99.521,
    "text": "♫ When you're with your friends"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.522,
    "endTime": 102.41300000000001,
    "text": "♫ And your family doing things"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.413,
    "endTime": 104.294,
    "text": "♫ Everywhere you look"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.294,
    "endTime": 106.521,
    "text": "♫ Everywhere you go ♫"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.522,
    "endTime": 110.203,
    "text": "- [Voiceover] That's all I-- I know these lyrics are completely wrong but--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.203,
    "endTime": 111.641,
    "text": "♫ Saxophone ♫"
  }
]